Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.85,0:00:04.72,Signs,,0,0,0,,Line Natsuhabara Station
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.34,0:00:13.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, geezer!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.11,0:00:16.00,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Hurry your ass up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.27,0:00:15.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was interesting, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.32,0:00:18.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Get a move on already!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.32,0:00:19.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.82,0:00:21.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a rude man.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.50,0:00:32.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A pickpocket!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.67,0:00:34.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone, catch him!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.79,0:00:36.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The guy from earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.04,0:00:36.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So he's a pickpocket?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.59,0:00:39.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.63,0:00:42.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.51,0:00:46.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Careful, boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.08,0:00:48.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.82,0:01:02.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mister...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.62,0:01:07.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll take a report there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.24,0:01:07.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you too...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.45,0:01:10.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.84,0:01:18.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.41,0:01:22.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.93,0:01:29.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After a while, we were released from police questioning.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.97,0:01:32.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We reboarded the Touto Loop Line, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.94,0:01:36.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh, what's going on there?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.82,0:01:44.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Three stations ahead is Sugame Station, and\Nan incident has already occurred nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.30,0:02:06.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we continue lamenting the passing seasons...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.24,0:02:07.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll be unable to confront the mysteries of cases!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.12,0:02:11.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The identity of the Friend of Justice\Nis actually a picture-story showman?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.81,0:02:13.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perceiving the one and only truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.48,0:02:15.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The appearance of a child and the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.27,0:02:17.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is: Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.75,0:03:54.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This guy is Kanemura, a wanted criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.05,0:03:57.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's a member of that fraud group, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.34,0:03:58.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.42,0:04:01.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By gaining the trust and favor of the elderly living alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.90,0:04:06.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He introduced them to fictitious investment\Nschemes and cheated them out of their money.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.50,0:04:10.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Many victims have committed suicide of filed bankruptcy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.37,0:04:11.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cause of death?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.75,0:04:13.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A blow to his forehead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.52,0:04:15.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the only wound on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.81,0:04:19.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think the culprit was pretty impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.02,0:04:23.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because there's no sign of a struggle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.02,0:04:25.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And to beat down such strong-looking man in one blow...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.36,0:04:28.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.53,0:04:29.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We saw this from the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.65,0:04:32.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, let's not bother them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.74,0:04:34.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.80,0:04:36.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You are...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.67,0:04:39.92,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,You guys are from earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.71,0:04:39.91,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Norizuki Tokuma (75)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.79,0:04:43.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you acquaintances?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.50,0:04:45.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, kind of...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.17,0:04:47.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why are you here, mister?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.96,0:04:50.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's our witness for this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.55,0:05:00.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After I parted ways with you earlier, I saw that\Nman hitting someone with a club from the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.52,0:05:03.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I deboarded at Beika Station and went to the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.56,0:05:07.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So he's the leader of the fraud group, Kiriya Teruhiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.23,0:05:08.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was there a falling out?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.03,0:05:13.16,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Kiriya Teruhiko (35)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.08,0:05:11.23,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I have nothing to do with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.28,0:05:13.16,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I was only taking a walk around here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.82,0:05:16.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He witnessed the scene from the train?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.97,0:05:18.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.58,0:05:21.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, mister, where's your cane?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.71,0:05:26.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since I can still move about without it, I left it somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.38,0:05:31.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Though it's convenient to have with me, since\Npeople think of me as elderly and are extra nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.55,0:05:36.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A single blow to the forehead killed the victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.18,0:05:40.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And this old man said he witnessed the scene from the train...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.89,0:05:43.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.10,0:05:45.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How many times do I have to repeat myself!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.35,0:05:47.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.32,0:05:51.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then why were you around the scene?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.61,0:05:54.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone called me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.49,0:05:56.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He claimed to be Kanemura's friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.91,0:05:58.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Saying Kanemura's waiting for me and to come now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.99,0:06:00.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A friend of the victim?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.99,0:06:01.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.20,0:06:03.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.41,0:06:04.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd never heard his voice before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.37,0:06:07.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't very well believe that story of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.92,0:06:09.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.43,0:06:10.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.63,0:06:12.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've been framed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.68,0:06:17.44,Signs,,0,0,0,,KIRIYA TERUHIKO (35)\NSUSPECT
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.68,0:06:17.44,Signs,,0,0,0,,******************
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.68,0:06:17.44,Signs,,0,0,0,,KILLING BETWEEN COMRADES?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.43,0:06:18.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A picture-story showman?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.14,0:06:19.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That old man is?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.64,0:06:20.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.64,0:06:23.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was investigating another case when I heard it from the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.93,0:06:27.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like he often performs for the\Nkids at places like Sasanqua Park.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.23,0:06:29.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.44,0:06:32.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, this case is almost as good as solved.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.32,0:06:34.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No need for a great detective to intervene.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.24,0:06:37.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If only everything would go smoothly...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.99,0:06:43.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true that I met with Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} here yesterday, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.83,0:06:46.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't know he was interested in this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.04,0:06:50.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At any rate, he wanted you to look into\Nwhat I just said as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.09,0:06:53.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.84,0:06:56.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now to get down to business.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.59,0:07:01.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"The Earth is now mine!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.68,0:07:03.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"I won't let you have it, Dark Lord!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.85,0:07:07.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"That voice can't be..."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.06,0:07:09.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Friend of Justice, on stage!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.94,0:07:13.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Dark Lord, time to face the punishment of justice!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.78,0:07:16.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.03,0:07:20.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Damn you, have a taste of this!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.28,0:07:25.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Having said that, the Lord's cane starts to release a black light!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.37,0:07:31.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look out, Friend of Justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.38,0:07:32.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Move it, move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.67,0:07:33.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wanna see it too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.84,0:07:34.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.59,0:07:35.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,HEY!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.51,0:07:36.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.80,0:07:39.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyone who comes late is at the back of the line!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.39,0:07:49.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,HEY!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.45,0:07:50.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Apologize before you cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.06,0:07:55.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No matter if you're a child or an adult, you\Nneed to follow the correct path of a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.49,0:08:00.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.95,0:08:01.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.12,0:08:04.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good, you're a good kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.66,0:08:07.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone, can we let this boy watch too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.00,0:08:09.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.54,0:08:12.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, please let him sit in the middle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.13,0:08:13.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.38,0:08:16.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bye bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.80,0:08:19.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See you guys later, and take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.34,0:08:22.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"No matter if you're a child or an adult..."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.30,0:08:25.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You need to scold whoever deserves a scolding...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.26,0:08:28.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the kindness to forgive them is also important, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.14,0:08:31.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're that miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.10,0:08:37.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You helped me during that dangerous moment,\Nbut I forgot to say my thanks yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.07,0:08:38.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.82,0:08:40.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I forgot to give this back to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.95,0:08:42.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.70,0:08:45.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is Mitsu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} perhaps your wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.41,0:08:49.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wish she were, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.04,0:08:51.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She passed away because of illness a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.58,0:08:53.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.88,0:08:55.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't know about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.79,0:08:56.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.59,0:08:58.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you came here just for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.92,0:08:59.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.63,0:09:04.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wanted to ask you why you walked away without\Ntelling your name when the pickpocket was caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.89,0:09:08.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It wasn't necessary to make myself\Nknown with a simple act like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.68,0:09:10.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.64,0:09:14.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you made yourself known as the witness\Nof the subsequent crime, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.98,0:09:16.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.57,0:09:17.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.94,0:09:19.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because it was a murder case.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.90,0:09:22.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't just pretend I didn't see that, now could I, boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.57,0:09:26.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then why didn't you call the police right away?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.16,0:09:27.88,Signs,,0,0,0,,Sugame
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.50,0:09:27.88,Signs,,0,0,0,,Kozuka
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.17,0:09:27.88,Signs,,0,0,0,,Sawabukuro
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.75,0:09:27.88,Signs,,0,0,0,,East Sawabukuro
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.42,0:09:27.88,Signs,,0,0,0,,Beika
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.37,0:09:27.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why wait until Beika Station?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.45,0:09:32.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't have a cell phone, and the conductor wasn't nearby either.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.25,0:09:35.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you didn't try to get off midway?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.79,0:09:40.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hadn't thought about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.17,0:09:42.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you done, boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.01,0:09:44.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If so, I'll be on my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.68,0:09:48.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks again, young miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.98,0:09:56.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.98,0:09:58.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Glad you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.82,0:10:01.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've found out about the matter Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} requested.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.15,0:10:04.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About the victim of the fraud group...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.61,0:10:08.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems some of them were acquaintances with that elder, Norizuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.79,0:10:12.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In addition, he is a 5-dan in Kendo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.58,0:10:15.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold it right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.04,0:10:17.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is Dad suspecting that old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.25,0:10:19.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.21,0:10:20.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.92,0:10:23.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But wasn't the culprit already caught?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.51,0:10:26.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he still denies it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.18,0:10:28.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll talk to Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.22,0:10:30.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.14,0:10:34.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No good, I need to quickly find the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.23,0:10:39.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, there's actually one more thing\NUncle wanted you to investigate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.32,0:10:41.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.36,0:10:48.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The crime scene was between this\NNatsuhabara Station and Beika Station.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.00,0:10:51.50,Signs,,0,0,0,,Natsuhabara
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.00,0:10:51.50,Signs,,0,0,0,,Sugame
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.00,0:10:51.50,Signs,,0,0,0,,Beika
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.70,0:10:51.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's near Sugame Station.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.00,0:10:55.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A security camera...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.21,0:10:59.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I should have Detective Takagi check that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.23,0:11:16.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.86,0:11:18.86,Signs,,0,0,0,,***************************************
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.86,0:11:18.86,Signs,,0,0,0,,Notice\NWe are currently undergoing renovations\Nand apologize for the inconvenience\NSugame Station
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.91,0:11:28.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not there yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.24,0:11:30.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.03,0:11:32.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that's how it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.16,0:11:36.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, wake up, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.75,0:11:39.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't you say the case was as good as solved?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.46,0:11:41.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are you doubting that old man now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.92,0:11:43.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I never doubted!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.76,0:11:45.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then why...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.96,0:11:47.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I never doubted...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.51,0:11:49.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This beer would be tasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.26,0:11:52.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.35,0:11:55.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was punishment from God.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.47,0:11:58.99,Signs,,0,0,0,,Witness: A{\rHonorifics - Signs}-san{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.06,0:11:58.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That man made many elders cry in despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.56,0:12:02.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Must've simply been a punishment from a friend of justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.61,0:12:03.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mister...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.36,0:12:05.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.61,0:12:07.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We now take you back to the studio.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.82,0:12:10.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.11,0:12:11.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He really...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.16,0:12:18.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.25,0:12:22.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it's going to take a little longer for that matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.75,0:12:24.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But good timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.46,0:12:29.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've just discovered a new fact,\Nso could you relay it to Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.55,0:12:30.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A new fact?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.73,0:12:41.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.36,0:12:50.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mister, are you home?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.69,0:12:52.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mister?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.20,0:12:57.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A diary...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.08,0:13:01.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's one more guy in the fraud group?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.79,0:13:02.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.58,0:13:04.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Name's Motegi Takashi, 25 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.71,0:13:11.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He cheated a woman, who was an acquaintance of\Nthat elder Norizuki, out of a huge sum of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.22,0:13:15.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're trying to locate his residence,\Nbut we couldn't get hold of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.14,0:13:17.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective Takagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.43,0:13:19.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please tell me the old man's address.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.73,0:13:28.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.38,0:13:44.38,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Motegi Takashi (25)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.72,0:14:00.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.73,0:14:02.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.06,0:14:04.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.48,0:14:06.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Miss...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.36,0:14:16.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't believe it, so I had wanted to hear from you directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.28,0:14:17.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So when I went to your home...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.99,0:14:22.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I apologize for reading this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.25,0:14:24.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is Mitsu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s diary, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.55,0:14:27.75,Signs,,0,0,0,,**************
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.04,0:14:27.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then I found your entry...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.42,0:14:32.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's this all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.42,0:14:34.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Motegi Takashi, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.09,0:14:35.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're with the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.22,0:14:36.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're under our protection.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.35,0:14:39.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Police!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.72,0:14:40.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Protection?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.72,0:14:44.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That old man over there intends to take your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.56,0:14:46.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.06,0:14:48.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What now!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.40,0:14:50.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Inspector?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.03,0:14:55.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I heard your order from Takagi,\Nthat's why I issued the protection.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.86,0:14:59.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I never ordered Takagi to do anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.25,0:15:09.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Norizuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.71,0:15:13.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can never deceive the eyes of\Nthe great detective Mouri Kogorou.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.13,0:15:16.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yesterday, it was you who killed Kanemura, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.26,0:15:19.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri Kogorou?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.09,0:15:21.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.01,0:15:23.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was a witness to that incident, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.02,0:15:27.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's exactly what I felt suspicious about in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.02,0:15:31.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You said that you witnessed the crime from the train, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.94,0:15:38.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With the railway bridge being a straight line, there's no\Nway you could have seen the crime scene underneath.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.87,0:15:40.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.83,0:15:42.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.95,0:15:43.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.29,0:15:45.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This thing, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.87,0:15:52.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've borrowed this IC pass from him and had the record\Nchecked out at the Data Center of the Touto Loop Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.50,0:15:56.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had no reason to refuse, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.13,0:15:58.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And what did you find out?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.84,0:16:01.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before and after the time of the crime yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.35,0:16:04.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He entered the fare gate at Natsuhabara Station at 13:35...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.18,0:16:09.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And exited at Beika Station at 14:15, according to the records.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.98,0:16:11.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.15,0:16:12.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because that's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.86,0:16:15.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, that's rather strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.36,0:16:18.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The entering time is all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.53,0:16:20.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the exiting time is off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.53,0:16:25.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because of the pickpocket incident, Conan\Nand Ran got off at Hatabata Station.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.62,0:16:27.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you didn't get off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.83,0:16:30.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.75,0:16:33.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the train's arrival time at Beika Station?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.00,0:16:33.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's 14:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.75,0:16:35.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.96,0:16:39.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's 15 minutes earlier than what the record showed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.43,0:16:40.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.97,0:16:42.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.01,0:16:45.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He got off midway at Sugame Station and committed the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.64,0:16:46.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He then got on the next train.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.56,0:16:50.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that why there's a 15-minute loss?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.35,0:16:53.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's a very interesting speculation, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.56,0:16:57.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that were true, it would've shown up in the record as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.61,0:16:58.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.90,0:17:01.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There wasn't a record of his getting off and on at Sugame Station.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.32,0:17:05.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, why the fifteen-minute discrepancy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.12,0:17:09.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm embarrassed to say this, but being an\Nelder means frequent restroom trips.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.58,0:17:12.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I rushed to the restroom once I arrived at Beika Station.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.54,0:17:15.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I didn't exit the fare gate sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.50,0:17:17.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.38,0:17:20.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The truth was being filmed by the station camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.38,0:17:22.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean the security camera?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.51,0:17:24.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.39,0:17:27.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sugame Station is undergoing renovation,\Nso there shouldn't be a working camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.18,0:17:30.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you really knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.52,0:17:34.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wasn't that exactly why you chose to commit the crime there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.11,0:17:36.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One more thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.48,0:17:40.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because many elders utilize that station, you wouldn't stand out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.45,0:17:46.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, you called the victim under the railway\Nbridge near Sugame Station beforehand...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.70,0:17:50.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And got off the train without being taped by the camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.96,0:17:54.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You then assulted Kanemura, and boarded the train again...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.21,0:17:59.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In addition to calling Kiriya to the crime\Nscene and making him lose his alibi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.47,0:18:07.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then how was I supposed to get off and on\NSugame Station without leaving a record?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.10,0:18:12.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had Detective Takagi check out the footage\Nof the Natsuhabara Station security camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.60,0:18:14.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Natsuhabara Station camera?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.94,0:18:20.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the suspicious actions of Norizuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was caught on tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.73,0:18:25.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At that time, you entered the fare gate with your IC pass...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.20,0:18:27.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you backed out once and reentered.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.41,0:18:30.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did you reenter?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.45,0:18:35.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's because I didn't think my IC pass went through correctly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.83,0:18:38.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An elder like me is bad with machines...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.21,0:18:42.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that exactly what you would like us to think?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.30,0:18:43.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.97,0:18:48.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At that time, you prepared not only your\NIC pass but also a pre-purchased ticket.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.18,0:18:52.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ticket?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.64,0:18:56.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You first scanned your IC pass across the machine at the fare gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.06,0:19:00.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then you pretended to redo it, but took out your ticket...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.73,0:19:04.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And inserted it which was hidden in view under your IC pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.11,0:19:08.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After being pushed by that pickpocket\Nguy, you held onto the machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.62,0:19:10.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And retrieved the punched ticket.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.83,0:19:16.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then you boarded the train, got off at\NSugame Station, and committed the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.71,0:19:19.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You then purchased another ticket and boarded again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.67,0:19:25.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When you arrived at Beika Station, you used the same\NIC pass you used at Natsuhabara Station to exit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.55,0:19:31.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The ticket you bought at Natsuhabara Station had been\Ncollected at the Sugame Station where you got off midway.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.26,0:19:34.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your fingerprint should still be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.69,0:19:39.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Impressive, Mr. Detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.61,0:19:43.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I have done nothing wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.23,0:19:44.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's what you'd call karma...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.94,0:19:46.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A punishment from justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.78,0:19:47.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.62,0:19:50.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.46,0:20:03.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You scold those who deserve a scolding, but you\Nalso possessed the kindness to forgive people.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.80,0:20:05.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So why did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.76,0:20:11.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It merely means that there are deeds one can never forgive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.97,0:20:15.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you do it because Mitsu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}\Ndied of shock from being swindled?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.43,0:20:17.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.56,0:20:18.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's exactly it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.48,0:20:24.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It wasn't until I read Mitsu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s\Ndiary that I knew about the fraud.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.19,0:20:25.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't forgive them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.94,0:20:30.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why, that's why I wanted to deliver\Nthe punishment of justice unto them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.07,0:20:33.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I understand how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.20,0:20:36.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.75,0:20:39.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you had read Mitsu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s last words...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.67,0:20:40.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You would've realized it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.33,0:20:43.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Last words?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.01,0:20:49.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.22,0:20:54.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Friend of Justice taught me about forgiving people.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.72,0:20:59.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I decided to forgive the man who deceived me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.77,0:21:04.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To this old lady who lives alone, he had been really nice to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.73,0:21:07.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His smile at that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.57,0:21:11.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I still don't think that everything he did was part of the lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.49,0:21:15.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I shall believe that he will change his ways someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.99,0:21:19.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's unbearable to die hating someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.33,0:21:22.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Friend of Justice, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.00,0:21:25.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't know this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.29,0:21:28.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After I learned about Motegi and his gang, I was enraged...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.01,0:21:31.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I couldn't see anything else except resentment.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.47,0:21:34.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Some Friend of Justice I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.80,0:21:37.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I allowed myself to be blinded by hatred...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.35,0:21:42.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I didn't know about Mitsu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s true feeling!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.02,0:21:49.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She... forgave someone like me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.78,0:21:51.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She trusted me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.41,0:21:56.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just like Ran said...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.99,0:22:01.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are things one cannot do no matter the circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.33,0:22:03.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not as a friend of justice...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.71,0:22:06.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rather, as a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.79,0:23:29.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Motegi confessed to everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.96,0:23:33.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And Kiriya was re-arrested on account\Nof malicious fraudulent intent.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.72,0:23:38.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please step back and touch the scanner again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.51,0:23:40.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.18,0:23:43.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Must be a malfunction.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.31,0:23:46.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I say IC is unreliable.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.98,0:23:47.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.94,0:23:50.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that the card from the rental video store?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.03,0:23:54.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.15,0:23:57.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uncle, aren't you the most unreliable?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.55,0:24:01.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tatezato Mika.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.27,0:24:03.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.03,0:24:08.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This woman is a murderer on the run,\Nand she wants to meet with Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.08,0:24:09.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.37,0:24:11.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.73,0:24:21.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then this incident was indeed...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.75,0:24:23.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The work of the kappa, wasn't it!?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.84,0:24:33.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.33,0:24:34.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shoe
